          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Market prices often exhibit boom-bust cycles with multiple turning points. Polynomial fitting captures these direction changes but beware: polynomial extrapolation far beyond the data can produce wild swings.</p>
