          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Projectile motion under gravity follows a perfect parabola. The quadratic model captures this exactly, with the vertex at the peak height. This is an ideal case where the mathematical model matches the physical law precisely.</p>
